00:17:11,691 --> 00:17:15,976
Oh, no, no, goddammit!
It's not supposed to go this way!

245
00:17:15,977 --> 00:17:17,203
What isn't?

246
00:17:17,204 --> 00:17:22,482
OK, Ruth, I'm graduating from The Plan tomorrow,

247
00:17:22,483 --> 00:17:25,588
and I would really like it if you would be my witness.

248
00:17:25,589 --> 00:17:27,770
The Plan? What is The Plan?

249
00:17:27,771 --> 00:17:30,171
It's a multi-disciplined course that allows you

250
00:17:30,172 --> 00:17:32,640
to think way beyond yourself,

251
00:17:32,641 --> 00:17:36,858
and rebuild your life, from the ground floor,
plank by plank.

252
00:17:36,859 --> 00:17:38,665
That sounds awful!

253
00:17:38,881 --> 00:17:41,954
It teaches you how to feel really good about yourself

254
00:17:41,955 --> 00:17:44,728
and get what you want out of life.

255
00:17:44,829 --> 00:17:46,344
Do you want to go?

256
00:17:46,345 --> 00:17:53,461
It would really mean a lot to me, Ruth.

257
00:18:09,908 --> 00:18:11,924
- Wow!
