288
00:19:50,993 --> 00:19:53,303
Whoa! Working out a little aggression there?

289
00:19:53,304 --> 00:19:57,168
We're having chicken piccatta.
It needs to marinate over night.

290
00:19:57,169 --> 00:20:01,182
You never cook like this for me.
You never even cook.

291
00:20:01,811 --> 00:20:05,743
And when Trevor goes back to New Haven,
I need you to forget that I can!

292
00:20:05,744 --> 00:20:07,995
