we're not interested in selling.

320
00:22:24,100 --> 00:22:27,386
Oh, Matt Gilardi is no longer with Kroehner.

321
00:22:27,685 --> 00:22:29,860
Yup. I fired his worthless ass,

322
00:22:29,861 --> 00:22:33,002
