that he was representing our company.

323
00:22:33,003 --> 00:22:35,197
And that is why I'm here today.

324
00:22:35,198 --> 00:22:41,163
To do a little damage control,
and apologize to you boys.

325
00:22:41,164 --> 00:22:42,239
Right.

326
00:22:42,240 --> 00:22:44,055
Oh, I don't blame you for not trusting me.

327
00:22:44,056 --> 00:22:46,439
