328
00:22:46,640 --> 00:22:49,754
- Cream with three sugars.
- Well, thank you.

329
00:22:50,032 --> 00:22:52,537
You didn't put rat poison in here, did you?

330
00:22:52,538 --> 00:22:55,334
Drink it and find out.

331
00:22:57,060 --> 00:22:58,889
Oh, please!

332
00:22:58,890 --> 00:23:02,899
You boys aren't afraid of Big Bad Mitzi,
