333
00:23:03,300 --> 00:23:04,583
Come on.

334
00:23:04,584 --> 00:23:06,821
The economy is in a tail spin.

335
00:23:06,822 --> 00:23:11,273
Corporations are downsizing, and resizing,
and reorganizing,

336
00:23:11,274 --> 00:23:12,455
including Kroehner.

337
00:23:12,456 --> 00:23:15,867
