Honey, we've got problems of our own.

338
00:23:15,868 --> 00:23:18,001
Okay, let's just cut the foreplay.

339
00:23:18,002 --> 00:23:19,792
But that's the best part.

340
00:23:19,793 --> 00:23:21,594
