341
00:23:21,595 --> 00:23:23,565
We despise everything you stand for:

342
00:23:23,566 --> 00:23:25,769
corporate profits over personal service,

343
00:23:25,770 --> 00:23:27,580
stockholders over clients,

344
00:23:27,581 --> 00:23:29,219
greed over everything else,

345
00:23:29,220 --> 00:23:31,081
so I think you should take
your gesture of good faith,

346
00:23:31,082 --> 00:23:33,542
and shove it up your ass!

347
00:23:34,482 --> 00:23:36,602
Ooh, well that's one opinion.

348
00:23:36,603 --> 00:23:39,607
Anything that you would care to add, David?

349
00:23:39,608 --> 00:23:43,412
No, I think Nate pretty much summed our position up.

350
00:23:44,308 --> 00:23:46,591
Well, alrighty then.

351
00:23:47,554 --> 00:23:50,086
I'll just show myself out.

352
00:23:53,218 --> 00:23:56,776
By the way, you might want to clean out your coffeemaker.

353
00:23:56,777 --> 00:23:59,229
Your coffee sucks.

354
00:24:03,091 --> 00:24:04,642
This is not so good.

355
00:24:04,749 --> 00:24:09,554
Well, who the fuck is named Mitzi anyway?
That sounds like something you name a fuckin' chiuaua!

356
00:24:19,224 --> 00:24:21,264
Pretty bitchin', huh?

357
00:24:21,809 --> 00:24:25,352
