and I treat people like shit.

430
00:29:55,194 --> 00:29:58,837
Like I treated myself for the last 30 years.

431
00:29:59,038 --> 00:30:01,944
But then I swear I'm going to win this.

432
00:30:02,145 --> 00:30:08,717
I'm going to build the life that
I always wanted to live.

433
00:30:18,272 --> 00:30:20,540
I thought it was too late.

434
00:30:21,269 --> 00:30:23,503
Two terrible marriages.

435
00:30:23,704 --> 00:30:29,009
Children who won't even return my phone calls.

436
00:30:29,210 --> 00:30:30,774
It hurts.

437
00:30:30,975 --> 00:30:34,487
I'm 41 and I feel like I'm 80.

438
00:30:35,016 --> 00:30:37,115
But I have value.

439
00:30:38,363 --> 00:30:40,622
I'm still here.

440
00:30:40,925 --> 00:30:44,297
And as long as I believe in myself

441
00:30:44,398 --> 00:30:47,603
and speak fiercely from the Eye,

442
00:30:47,904 --> 00:30:50,053
then there's still hope.

443
00:30:50,054 --> 00:30:53,092
